{
  "name": "DT Platform — SRE Operations",
  "version": 21,
  "variables": [],
  "tiles": {
    "0": {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "## DT Platform — SRE Operations\nGolden Signals dashboard (Rate · Errors · Duration) for the platform engineering team. All charts reflect OneAgent-instrumented services — no SDK changes required."
    },
    "1": {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "### SRE Golden Signals\n\n**R**ate\nRequests per minute\n\n---\n\n**E**rrors\nFailed request %\n\n---\n\n**D**uration\np50 / p95 / p99 latency\n\n---\n\n**Soak test indicators**\n- JVM heap climbing = memory leak\n- GC time increasing = heap pressure\n- DB call duration rising = connection pool exhaustion"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "Rate — Requests / min by Service",
      "type": "data",
      "query": "timeseries count = sum(dt.service.request.count), by:{dt.entity.service}",
      "visualization": "lineChart",
      "visualizationSettings": {
        "chartSettings": {
          "legend": { "hidden": false }
        },
        "thresholds": []
      },
      "querySettings": {
        "maxResultRecords": 1000,
        "defaultScanLimitGbytes": 500,
        "maxResultMegaBytes": 1,
        "defaultSamplingRatio": 10,
        "enableSampling": false
      },
      "davis": {
        "enabled": false,
        "davisVisualization": { "isAvailable": true }
      }
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "Errors — Failed Request Rate % by Service",
      "type": "data",
      "query": "timeseries {total = sum(dt.service.request.count), failed = sum(dt.service.request.failure_count)}, by:{dt.entity.service} | fieldsAdd failure_rate = arrayMap(failed, (v, i) -> if(total[i] > 0, (v / total[i]) * 100.0, else: 0.0))",
      "visualization": "lineChart",
      "visualizationSettings": {
        "chartSettings": {
          "legend": { "hidden": false }
        },
        "thresholds": []
      },
      "querySettings": {
        "maxResultRecords": 1000,
        "defaultScanLimitGbytes": 500,
        "maxResultMegaBytes": 1,
        "defaultSamplingRatio": 10,
        "enableSampling": false
      },
      "davis": {
        "enabled": false,
        "davisVisualization": { "isAvailable": true }
      }
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "Duration — Response Time p50 / p95 / p99",
      "type": "data",
      "query": "timeseries {p50 = percentile(dt.service.response_time, 50), p95 = percentile(dt.service.response_time, 95), p99 = percentile(dt.service.response_time, 99)}",
      "visualization": "lineChart",
      "visualizationSettings": {
        "chartSettings": {
          "legend": { "hidden": false }
        },
        "thresholds": []
      },
      "querySettings": {
        "maxResultRecords": 1000,
        "defaultScanLimitGbytes": 500,
        "maxResultMegaBytes": 1,
        "defaultSamplingRatio": 10,
        "enableSampling": false
      },
      "davis": {
        "enabled": false,
        "davisVisualization": { "isAvailable": true }
      }
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "Host CPU Usage %",
      "type": "data",
      "query": "timeseries cpu_usage = avg(dt.host.cpu.usage), by:{dt.entity.host}",
      "visualization": "lineChart",
      "visualizationSettings": {
        "chartSettings": {
          "legend": { "hidden": false }
        },
        "thresholds": []
      },
      "querySettings": {
        "maxResultRecords": 1000,
        "defaultScanLimitGbytes": 500,
        "maxResultMegaBytes": 1,
        "defaultSamplingRatio": 10,
        "enableSampling": false
      },
