      "querySettings": {
        "maxResultRecords": 1000,
        "defaultScanLimitGbytes": 500,
        "maxResultMegaBytes": 1,
        "defaultSamplingRatio": 10,
        "enableSampling": false
      },
      "davis": {
        "enabled": false,
        "davisVisualization": { "isAvailable": true }
      }
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "Database Call Duration — Connection Pool Health",
      "type": "data",
      "query": "timeseries db_duration = avg(dt.service.dbcall.duration), by:{dt.entity.service}",
      "visualization": "lineChart",
      "visualizationSettings": {
        "chartSettings": {
          "legend": { "hidden": false }
        },
        "thresholds": []
      },
      "querySettings": {
        "maxResultRecords": 1000,
        "defaultScanLimitGbytes": 500,
        "maxResultMegaBytes": 1,
        "defaultSamplingRatio": 10,
        "enableSampling": false
      },
      "davis": {
        "enabled": false,
        "davisVisualization": { "isAvailable": true }
      }
    },
    "10": {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "### Soak Test Signatures\n\n**Memory leak:**\n- JVM Heap: steadily climbing (should be flat)\n- GC Suspension: trending upward over time\n\n**Connection pool exhaustion:**\n- DB Call Duration: rising after 15-20 min\n- Response Time p95: slowly drifting up\n\n**Run:**\n```\nmake soak-short APP_HOST=<ip>  # 5 min\nmake soak APP_HOST=<ip>         # 30 min\n```\n\n➡ [View Problems](/ui/problems)"
    }
  },
